dct_title_s: Map of the Colorado Delta showing the Imperial Canal System : constructed and owned by the California Development Company
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. "Imperial Land Company, Gen. Agents." Shows only the southeastern portion of the county, the area around the town of Imperial. Lands "filed under Imperial Canal System" shown in red; canals, rivers and lakes shown in blue. Includes "Marginal map showing location of irrigable lands."
